# Gayifiers iOS App — Start Here

Before any task, read **`HANDOVER.md`** in this repo root.

## This repo (iOS App)

- **Stack:** Expo SDK 54 · EAS Build · App Store Connect
- **Path:** `~/Projects/app.gayifiers` only — **never** `~/Developer/app.gayifiers`
- **Build:** commit first → `eas build` → `eas submit` (build alone does not upload to Connect)
- **Bundle ID:** `com.uncletullio.gayifiers` · App ID **6758533618**

## EAS quota (conserve builds)

- iOS builds are limited (e.g. 15/month on free tier)
- **Do not** run `eas build` without user approval after local testing
- ERRORED builds still count toward quota

## App Store v1.0 scope

- Bangkok mock · no login · no Trending/Plus/IAP
- `supportsTablet: false` (iPhone only)
- Do not re-add `app/index.tsx` with `<Redirect />` (TestFlight black screen)

